Tetratrichobothrius flavicaudis (De Geer, 1778)
( Fig. 50 ; Fet & Soleglad, 2002; Jacob et al., 2004b ; Vachon, 1948). It has been reported to be present in 6 species of Alpiscorpius Gantenbein et al., 1999 (
